{
  "texts": [
    "Section 4 outlines the cross-validation procedure employed to assess the models' predictive performance and presents results using real data at regional level.",
    "Section 5 extends these findings by reporting the corresponding national-level results.",
    "The paper concludes with a discussion.",
    "This study uses lung cancer incidence and mortality data for males in England.",
    "The data is stratified by the 106 clinical commissioning groups (CCG) (see Figure 1) and covers the period from 2001 to 2019."
  ]
}